# z0-auth

## Product

Self-hosted IAM for app developers (Auth0/Clerk-like): apps, OAuth/OIDC, hosted `/auth`, console admin. Browser apps use PKCE; server apps use confidential clients. [docs/product.md](../../docs/product.md).

## Stack

Bun monolith (`/api`, `/auth`, `/oauth`, React console). Specs in `docs/api/`. Work tracked in **Todoist Auth** only.

